China’s Defense Ministry to Hold Monthly Press Conferences

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-04-27T15:25:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/china-s-defense-ministry-to-hold-monthly-press-conferences.html
China ’s Ministry of National
Defense will start holding monthly press conferences this month,
the government said in a statement on its website today.  The briefings on the last Wednesday of every month will
help facilitate communication between the ministry and the
media, and will help the world understand China’s military
better, it said in the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Liza Lin in Shanghai at 
